

* 表结构
| model_name        | collection_name   | field      | help_text      |
|-------------------+-------------------+------------+----------------|
| BusinessCategory  | business_category | level      | 分类级别       |
|                   |                   | parent     | 父分类id       |
|                   |                   | name       | 分类名         |
|                   |                   | code       | 分类code(0101) |
|                   |                   | color      | 分类对应的颜色 |
|-------------------+-------------------+------------+----------------|
| BusinessVillage   | business_village  | business   | 对应商家id     |
|                   |                   | village    | 对应小区id     |
|                   |                   | category   | 对应商家分类   |
|-------------------+-------------------+------------+----------------|
| Business          | business          | name       | 商家名陈       |
|                   |                   | alias_name | 商家别名       |
|                   |                   | longitude  | 经度           |
|                   |                   | latitude   | 维度           |
|                   |                   | uid        | 标识数据来源   |
|                   |                   | address    | 商家地址       |
|                   |                   | telephone  | 商家号码       |
|                   |                   | status     | 状态           |
|                   |                   | category   | 商家分类标签   |
|-------------------+-------------------+------------+----------------|
| BusinessCorrect   | business_correct  | business   | 对应商家id     |
|                   |                   | user       | 对应纠错用户   |
|                   |                   | content    | 纠错内容       |
|-------------------+-------------------+------------+----------------|
| SecondTransaction | transactions      |            |                |
